Setup:

* Install cpanminus: https://github.com/miyagawa/cpanminus
* Install deps (cpanm --installdeps .)
* Run script/bigscreen_deploy.pl to deploy the database schema
* Run plackup to start the application.
* Visit http://localhost:5000/admin to setup delegates, districts and agenda
* Visit http://<your-ip>:5000/ from the computer you want to show on a bigscreen
